Frederic B. Luddy 
Executive Compensation
As Former Chief Product Officer, Director at SERVICENOW INC, Frederic B. Luddy  made $5,575,855 in total compensation.  Of this total $266,538 was received as a salary, $297,743 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $5,008,000 was awarded as stock and $3,574 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


