Frederic B. Luddy

Age : 60Public asset : 218,716,690 USDLinked companies : No connection available 





Summary 



Mr. Frederic B. Luddy is on the Board of Directors at ServiceNow, Inc. Mr. Luddy was previously employed as Chief Technology Officer by Peregrine Systems, Inc., Product Author by Amdahl Corp., Architect by Boole & Babbage, Inc., Founder by Enterprise Software, Inc., Chief Architect by Remedy Corp., and Chief Architect by Service Centers Corp.



